data.text:
Kerry Katona reveals her fiance has a free pass to have a baby with someone else

Stephen Gately is always with me, says Keith Duffy as he opens up on Boyzone future

The ex-Westlife star had two children with wife Kerry Katona before a very acrimonious split in 2004. He was engaged to Australian singer Delta Goodrem but they split in 2011. He went on to marry Irish model Vogue Williams but they split in 2015. He pursued a solo singing career after Westlife and also hosts TV and radio shows.
